_sText:
This pack was inspired by Just Cause 2, it is my second ever prefab release!  This pack is basically intended to help add detail to your maps, it focuses on a middle eastern setting and provides a variety of different prefabs for your use!  Feel free to modify my prefabs to the needs of your map, I made them so they are intentionally easy to modify for your own needs! The map displayed in the screenshots is a showcase map intended to demonstrate the prefabs (not all of them are in the map).

Note I: Please Credit me on release of your map if you use one of my prefabs, (Terrora).

Note II: Some of the buildings are variations of each other, this isn't a cheap way to add more content easily its the same with any game they re-use their assets wherever possible!

Contents:
- 7 Unique Detailed Big Buildings
- 2 Petrol Stations
- 2 Smaller Houses
- 1 Garage
- 3 Types of Fencing
- 1 Telephone Box
- 3 Billboards
- 4 Concrete Barriers
- 2 Wooden Barriers

Thanks Alex (Terrora / Roluffy)
